## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-114"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A>建構函式初始化<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-114">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor initializes the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-115">識別碼必須是唯一指定的文法項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-115">The identifier must be unique within a given grammar.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-116"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A>建構函式會擲回<xref:System.FormatException>在下列情況：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-116">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor throws a <xref:System.FormatException> in the following circumstances:</span></span>  
  
