 <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-153"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>物件可能也會包含<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsNameValueTag>和<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag>將語意值和語意索引鍵新增至規則的物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-153">An <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object may also contain <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsNameValueTag> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag> objects that add semantic values and semantic keys to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-154">語音辨識引擎會傳回語意的資訊，以及已辨識的片語，它會辨識片語時。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-154">The speech recognition engine will return the semantic information, as well as the recognized phrase, when it recognizes the phrase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-155">請參閱[語意的解譯標記](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/2e115391-73b3-4666-8fd1-540c529de3b0)如需詳細資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-155">See [Semantic Interpretation Markup](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/2e115391-73b3-4666-8fd1-540c529de3b0) for more information.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-156">下列範例會建立可辨識片語的文法"曾榮獲世界盃民族 is"再加上贏得世界盃比賽的國家/地區名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-156">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-157">在建立後<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>物件`winnerRule`並提供字串識別碼`WorldCupWinner`，此範例會使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A>方法，將附加的字串 「 贏得比賽世界盃國家/地區 」 規則。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-157">After creating the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object `winnerRule` and giving it the string identifier `WorldCupWinner`, the example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> method to append the string  "A nation that has won the World Cup is" to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-158">這個範例會建立兩個其他規則，請`ruleEurope`和`ruleSAmerica`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-158">The example then creates two additional rules, `ruleEurope` and  `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-159">使用重新<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A>方法，此範例會附加<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>物件`WorldCupWinner`包含的規則參考的規則`ruleEurope`和`ruleSAmerica`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-159">Again using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> method, the example appends an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object to the `WorldCupWinner` rule that contains rule references to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
// and set its scope to public.  
SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
// Add the introduction.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
// Create the rule for the European nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
// Create the rule for the South American nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
// Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
// Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
// the root rule of the document.  
document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
document.Root = winnerRule;  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-186">範圍的預設值是`Private`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-186">The default value for scope is `Private`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-187">從在其包含文法根規則或參考的根規則的另一個規則的規則參考只針對辨識啟用私用的規則。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-187">A private rule can only be activated for recognition by a rule reference from the root rule in its containing grammar or from another rule that is referenced from the root rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-188">私用的規則無法參考之外部文法，除非其包含文法根規則宣告私用的規則。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-188">A private rule cannot be referenced by an external grammar, unless the private rule is declared as the root rule of its containing grammar.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-189">如果其範圍設為`Public`，則<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>可以針對辨識啟用物件，參考從<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef>物件中包含的文法，或來自外部文法中的規則。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-189">If its scope is set to `Public`, an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object can be activated for recognition by a reference from a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> object in the containing grammar or from a rule in an external grammar.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-190">下列範例會建立可辨識片語的文法"曾榮獲世界盃民族 is"再加上贏得世界盃比賽的國家/地區名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-190">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-191">它會建立名為公用規則`WorldCupWinner`並將該規則的範圍設為公用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-191">It creates a public rule named `WorldCupWinner` and sets the scope of that rule to Public.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule and set its scope to public.  
SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
// Add the introduction.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
// Create the rule for the European nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
// Create the rule for the South American nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
// Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope)), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica)})));  
  
// Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
// the root rule of the document.  
document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
document.Root = winnerRule;  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d1f16-192">建立的文法的格式如下。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1f16-192">The created grammar has the following form.</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<grammar version="1.0" xml:lang="en-US" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/06/grammar" root="WorldCupWinner">  
    <rule id="WorldCupWinner" scope="public">  
        <item> A nation that has won the world cup is </item>  
        <one-of>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#EuropeanNations" />  
            </item>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#SouthAmericanNations" />  
            </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="EuropeanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> England< /item>  
            <item> France </item>  
            <item> Germany </item>  
            <item> Italy </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="SouthAmericanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> Argentina </item>  
            <item> Brazil </item>  
            <item> Uruguay </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
</grammar>  
```
